  "name": "Poisonous Lock [A]",
  "type": "consumable",
  "img": "icons/commodities/treasure/broach-skull-dagger-grey.webp",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You create a sprint loaded lock with a poisoned spine near the keyhole.</p><p>Breaking this lock does not disengage the poison spine.</p><p>A creature that attempts to unlock or pick this lock without the correct key triggers this trap.</p><p>When this trap is triggered, the triggering creature is stabbed with the poisoned spine forcing them to make a saving throw.</p><p>On a failed save they are poisoned and envenomed for 1 hour.</p><p>A creature who fails their saving throw by 5 or more, instead gains 3 ranks of envenomed.</p><p></p><p>Build DC: 27</p><p>Notice/Disable DC: 21</p><p>Toolkit Req to create/disable: Poison kit</p>",
